    <abstract id="aspace_13be163c4e034df65c3bdc4feb5b1e59">This collection contains University of Pittsburgh Department of Physiology staff meeting minutes from 1961 to 1981 and documents the development of the program while it was led by Dr. Ernst Knobil.</abstract>
