  <scopecontent id="aspace_9a13e5bafc3314cc54923c0ad59a25cd">
    <head>Scope and Content Notes</head>
<p>This collection of Physiology Department staff meeting minutes and photographs belonged to the R.B. Mellon Chair of Physiology, Dr. Ernst Knobil. Spanning from 1961 to 1981, his entire time as the founding chair, these minutes and articles from university publications document the progress of the department as it developed into one of the nation's best physiology programs.</p>  </scopecontent>
